title: Gypsy for Tadoba safari information needed
text: # 2 hi, you can call Subhash Guide. He has two new Gypsies. He will also give you good experienced Guides. His number is 080552 57451 Or you can call Nirav rawal .. He is Gypsy owner and he stays at Chandrapur. His number is 9850453078 For any other help you can contact me any time. I have been to Tadoba 10 times. Gypsy Charges are approx Rs 3000 per trip that includes Gypsy charges 2000 plus Guide and Driver charges and Jungle charges by Forest department. All Gypsywalas take same charges. regards,
